This program was made on a system with the following specifications:
System                    : Dell Inspiron-5458
OS                        : Ubuntu 18.04 Bionic Beaver
Ram                       : 8GB
Internal memory           : 1TB
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Prerequisites

node.js v8.10.0
mongodb v3.6.3
npm v3.5.2
npm modules{
              express
              body-parser
              mongodb
              jade
              path
              assert
           }
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation

To install the dependencies and application run the "install.sh" file as "./install.sh" (withtout "") in the terminal.
Once everything is installed run the file "start.sh" as "./start.sh" (withtout "").

Note: The program can also be started by navigating to the folder via terminal and running "node server.js"(withtout "").
